Setting the vapi files up:

sudo cp /usr/share/vala-0.12/vapi/libnotify.vapi /usr/share/vala/vapi/libnotify.vapi
sudo cp /usr/share/vala-0.12/vapi/vte.vapi /usr/share/vala/vapi/vte-2.90.vapi

Needed:
valac-0.12
libgtk-3-dev
libvte-2.90-dev
libnotify-dev

Compile with:
valac --pkg gtk+-3.0 --pkg vte-2.90 --pkg notify main.vala -o pantheon-terminal
